{
  "chapter": 55,
  "chapter_summary": "杨钲父子逃入森林后巧遇欧阳伯和，得知叶总督兵败、归德堡被农民起义占领的消息。李光夏一行发现杨钲与欧阳伯和，双方交手。江海天携仲长统、上官泰赶到，三大高手压阵。上官泰与杨钲单打独斗，杨钲求饶未果，趁上官泰一念仁慈偷袭，被上官泰大手印重伤后逃跑时摔死。仲长统与欧阳伯和激战近千招，欧阳伯和使出两败俱伤的鹏搏九霄仍落败，武功被废，被耿秀凤求情后放走。叶凌风独自在森林逃亡，幻想以冷天禄人头换官职。叶慕华与耿秀凤在森林并辔追踪叶凌风，二人互诉衷肠，感情升温。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叶凌风这小子简直是岂有此理，我非和他算帐不可。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_fan",
      "speaker_name": "杨梵",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "对啦，他现在也不是什么总督的少爷了，咱们已用不着怕他，他害得咱们吃了大亏，先捉住他出一口乌气。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_yang_fan",
      "text": "咱们还得隐忍些儿，待为父的迫他把江家的内功心法都吐了出来之后，那时再慢慢折磨他也还不迟。你可记得他是向哪一方跑的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_fan",
      "speaker_name": "杨梵",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "是向西方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "原来是杨二哥，这可真是巧遇了。我是给你烤的鹿肉的香气引来的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "欧阳大哥，你怎么也到这儿来了。我还想上你那儿避难呢。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "你要避什么难？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "唉，真是一言难尽。大哥，你且坐下来让小弟和你细说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "糟了，糟了！叶总督兵败，归德堡也回不去了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "为何归德堡也不能去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "归古愚一心效力朝廷，将他的团练都带了出来，编为官军。留守归德堡的只是老弱残兵和一部分家丁。归古愚以为他坐镇归德堡数十年，等于是土皇帝一般，堡中百姓畏威怀德，谁敢反他？他虽然离开，只凭着他的威望也还可以镇压得下的。哪知前几日他的堡中快马来报？庄稼汉不知受了谁的煽动，不怕归家的威风，竟然趁机会造起反来了。如今整个归德堡都被乱民占据，这个时候，还怎能去归德堡？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "哦，竟然有此等事？那么归古愚现在何处？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "归古愚将他的团练编成一军，得了总兵的官职，好不兴头，他奉了朝廷的命令，带兵增援时总督，会攻小金川。归古愚是打算攻下了小金川之后，再回师清乡，哪知叶总督先已全军覆没了，你说这不是糟糕透顶么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "这么说来，归古愚的这支军队岂不是正向着此方行进？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "不错，他的行军计划是通过这座森林以攻小金川之背。我是先来给他探听消息的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "他有多少兵力？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "约有一万多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "如今小金川和西昌都被叛军占领，叛军的势力比官军大得多了。归古愚这一万多人，不够人家一口吞掉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "事已如斯，且不管它，吃饱鹿肉，今晚先睡一觉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "林道轩",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "你是什么人？和杨钲是什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "我们不管你是什么人，只要你不插手，我们就不理你。我们要对付的只是姓杨的老贼。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "杨兄，这几个小娃娃口气倒是很大，你用得着我帮忙么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "欧阳大哥，拜托你照顾小儿。这几个小娃娃么，还不放在我的心上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "你是我们手下败将，胆敢口出大言？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "text": "你以为我当真是输给你们这几个小娃娃么？叫你知道我的厉害！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "你们这两个老贼，以大欺小，羞也不羞？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "师父，这个姓杨的老贼欺负我们，你可要替我们出一口气。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "text": "这两个人么，自有仲帮主和上官前辈找他们算帐的。用不着咱们动手，你们退下吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "师父，你的病都好了？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "林道轩",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "师父，你怎么来得这样快啊？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们走了七天之后，仲帮主和上官前辈来探我的病，他们是想到西昌去，顺便来向我辞行的。恰巧我的病已经痊愈，就和他们一同来了。嗯，是比我的预期要好得快一些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "咱们谊属连襟，想不到今日却成了生死冤家，这是小弟不合在前，也怪不得我兄。不过，我却想请上官兄看在亲戚的份上。网开一面。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "什么，你要向我讨饶？我可是不能饶你的！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "不，我得罪了襟兄，你要杀我，那是应该的。我纵不济，也何至于向你求饶？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "那你说什么网开一面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "小儿杨梵，年幼无知，也曾得罪了令媛和林公子。但他的罪过都应该由我承担，请上官兄看在亲戚份上，是否可以放他一条生路？他也曾经被林公子所伤了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "上官纨",
      "listener": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "text": "轩弟，你的意思怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "林道轩",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "text": "今日他已为我所伤，我若现在杀他，胜之不武。好，今日我可以饶他一命，下次碰上，就不能放过了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "上官纨",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "爹爹，轩弟这么说，那么，今日就让这小子走吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_fan",
      "text": "好，杨梵，你走！我不怕你为父报仇。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_fan",
      "speaker_name": "杨梵",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "爹爹，我还是陪着你吧。要死，咱们父子同死。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_fan",
      "speaker_name": "杨梵",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "爹爹，你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_yang_fan",
      "text": "傻孩子，留得青山在，哪怕没柴烧。你的姨父虽说与我决一死生，但说不定阎主爷还不肯收留我呢！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "要是你杀不了我，那又如何？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "不是你死，便是我亡。嘿，嘿，你怕我倚多为胜么？你也应该早知道我的为人了，我上官泰是这样的人么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "当然，当然。咱们是说好了单打独斗的。我岂能信不过你？梵儿，你走吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "老叫化不甘寂寞，看着别人交手，老叫化也心痒难熬了。欧阳山主，咱们也该算一算帐啦！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "text": "不错，你这臭叫化打伤了我的浑家，我正要与你算帐。听说你看不起我的雷神掌，我倒要看看你的混元一气功有怎么厉害？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "林道轩",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "text": "纨姐，咱们也来拆招玩玩。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "上官纨",
      "listener": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "text": "好，但你是男子，气力比我大，可得让我几分，我使剑，你用一根树枝吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "林道轩",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "text": "好的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "上官纨",
      "listener": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "text": "你不要夸嘴，且看我用家传的剑法破你。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "上官纨",
      "listener": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "text": "你瞧，我不是把你的剑法破了吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_dao_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "林道轩",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "text": "不见得，再接招！",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "咱们说好了是单打独斗的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "我要谁帮忙来了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "杨钲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "你的女儿——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "她自练本门剑法，又碍了你什么了？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "杨钲，你想跑已经迟啦！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "杨钲，你还要顽抗么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "上官纨",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "爹爹，你怎可让他！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_yang_zheng",
      "text": "杨怔，你当真是至死不悟么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当真是自作孽，不可活！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们看老叫化去。但愿他这一架还未打完。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仲帮主使得好一个混元一气功！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "江大侠，你看如何？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "仲帮主是不会败的，但要取胜只怕也是不易罢了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "师父，他们这样打法，不知要打到几时？咱们可还要去捉拿叶凌风这奸贼呢。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "text": "我不急，你们急什么？总不会打到明天的。有上官前辈和仲帮主与我分头搜捕，难道还怕他飞得上天？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "text": "仲帮主、手下留情！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "你这女娃儿要为你师公求情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "text": "正邪不两立，我怎敢阻挠帮主？但他今后己是不能作恶的了，他于我有传艺之恩，我这才胆敢请仲帮主饶他一命。仲帮主给我这个人情，就算是我还了师门的债吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "欧阳伯和，你惭不惭愧？我真想不到像你这样的好恶之人。居然有一个这样的好徒弟。你们夫妻俩设谋算计她，她却还在为你求侥！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "耿姑娘，你大约还不知道你的师公是为什么来的吧？他是要来迫你嫁给归古愚那个宝贝儿于的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "不过，看在你的份上，反正他的武功已废了，我就饶他一命吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "耿姑娘，多谢你啦。欧阳伯和得以苟延残喘，今生是不能报答姑娘你的了。但总有人会替我报答你的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "text": "你这话是什么意思，你想怎样？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "text": "我还能怎样？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳伯和",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多蒙帮主不杀之恩，我走啦！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "speaker_name": "仲长统",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "来，来，来，耿姑娘，我给你引见，这位就是名闻当世。武功天下第一的江海天江大侠。这位耿姑娘是后辈的女中英杰，当真说得上是出于污泥而不染——",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_zhong_chang_tong",
      "text": "仲帮主，你不必夸赞我啦，我正要江大侠帮忙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "帮什么忙呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "江大侠，你的侄儿在这儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "speaker_name": "江海天",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "我的侄儿？你是说叶凌风在这儿么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_jiang_hai_tian",
      "text": "不，不，我是说你真的那个侄儿，不是假冒的那个叶凌风。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我的爹爹也是这贼子与他的父亲合谋陷害的。如此说来，他们父子正是你我共同的仇人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "如今咱们是报仇在即，你还何用叹气？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "你有所不知，我、我是颇有感触。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "感触什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "叶凌风的爹爹是朝廷的大官，他们父子同恶相济，以致成为了义军的死对头。知道叶凌风的事情的英雄豪杰，也没有谁不想杀他的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "这不很好么？难道你还为他叹气？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "谁为了这奸贼叹气了？哦是为自己叹气！我、我是想到了自己的身世。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "我爹爹的官没有叶屠户做得大，但也曾经做过伊宁的总兵，也曾经打过汉族和哈萨克族的义军。呀，叶大哥，你对我好，我是知道的。就只怕你的朋友，未必都能像你一样，把我当作自己人。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "我以为你担心什么，原来担心这个。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "不值得担心么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "你的爹爹和叶凌风的爹爹都是朝廷的大官，手上或多或少沾过义军的鲜血。叶屠户心狠手辣，罪恶滔天；比你的爹爹大得多。但你的爹爹也是犯有罪恶的，这个不用为你的爹爹忌讳。可是，你和叶凌风却是完全两样，叶凌风与他的爹爹同恶相济，你如今却是义军的女首领，和你的爹爹走的是两条路。一个人的出身是不能自己作主的，但长大之后，立身处世，却是完全可以由自己作主了，你和叶凌风既然是完全两样，别人又怎会用同一的眼光来看你呢？即使暂时有点误会，终究也会明白的。好像冷铁樵大哥，后来不是深自引咎，向你道歉了么？你放心，我担保我的朋友都会把你当作自己人的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "你这么说，我就放心了。不满你说，我以前很为这几句俗语担忧，这几句俗语说的是：龙生龙，凤生凤，老鼠儿子会打洞。我怕别人相信这几句俗语，对我有异样的眼光。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "叶慕华",
      "listener": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "text": "这几句俗语是错的，明白事理的人绝不会受它影响的。你瞧瞧我的眼睛，我对你有异样的眼光么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_xiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "耿秀凤",
      "listener": "char_ye_mu_hua",
      "text": "哪有这样看人的，还说不是异样的眼光？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 55
    }
  ],
